Notes on the toy model 

1 ha or small plot model
they is no much work on how dispersal by harvesting works, and no agroecological managment. 
- this is important warning beacuse were not trying to propose to spray workers. no antyhing they would do or increase theire already exploitation situation. 
- So that is why it is good to think about proceudres that are applicable to small plots. 

--> so one thing is to characterize the movement

--> but the real questions for the toy model is:

Is harvesting relevant at all to rust dispersal anda general infection

How do:
- jumps vs no jumps change (and according to the size) affect the infection
- do avoiding plants affect anything? 

(planting pattern??)

--> we have the small jumps (within pante) and the big jumps between pante (this is more applicable to 1- 5 ha dough. A pante is like 25m x 25 m.) The big jump can go to 100 m jump!. We can say a 5 ha plot, harvested in one day. 

This is important because:

Plantation pattern --> affect cotact/splah dispersal, with random wind. 

Pkantation pattern --> harvesting pattern?? this is important (beacise it affects the small jumps)

We set 1.5 m for contact. 
